                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The large  solid-angle  LASA detector",
                " which  consists  of three concentric levels  of wires",
                " multiwire  proportional chambers,  surrounded  by two",
                " layers  of plastic scintillators  the inner  of which",
                " was 3-mm thick  dE-counter  and  the outer  was 25 mm",
                " thick E-counter."
              ]
            }
          ],
